<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>GNexus</title>

<style>
body{
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    text-align:center;
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    background:#ffffff;
    color:#111;
}

.container{
    padding:50px 20px;
}

img{
    width:180px;
    margin-bottom:20px;
}

h1{
    font-size:55px;
    margin-top:20px;
    max-width:700px;
    margin-left:auto;
    margin-right:auto;
}

p{
    font-size:22px;
    max-width:700px;
    margin:20px auto;
    line-height:1.5;
}

.btn{
    display:inline-block;
    margin-top:20px;
    padding:18px 35px;
    background:#0d6efd;
    color:#fff;
    text-decoration:none;
    border-radius:10px;
    font-size:22px;
}

footer{
    margin-top:80px;
    padding:30px;
    background:#f1f1f1;
    font-size:24px;
}

@media(max-width:768px){
    h1{
        font-size:38px;
    }

    p{
        font-size:18px;
    }

    .btn{
        font-size:18px;
        padding:15px 25px;
    }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
    <img src="logo.png" alt="GNexus">

    <h1>Conectamos sua marca ao crescimento</h1>

    <p>
        A GNexus conecta empresas, clientes e influenciadores
        através de estratégias inteligentes de marketing digital.
    </p>

    <a class="btn" href="https://wa.me/55 77 9820-9467">
        Falar no WhatsApp
    </a>
</div>

<footer>
    Instagram: @g.nexus7
</footer>

</body>
</html>
